				<p class="nyt-article-byline">By JENNA WORTHAM</p>
				<p class="nyt-article-summary">Hana Beshara was a founder of NinjaVideo, one of the most popular online sites for illegal TV and movie downloads. To the online community, she was its queen. To the government, she was simply a thief.</p>
